<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter">ho&s;e clear Wells where &s;weetne&s;s dwells,</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter">n up by Saints, in cry&s;tal Buckets.</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 word"> by that happy bli&s;sful way,</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter">e peaceful Pilgrims I &s;hall &s;ee,</L>
<L>a<GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter"> have ca&s;t off thei<GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter"> <GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter">ags o<GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter"> clay,</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter">d walk apparrel'd fre&s;h like me.</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter">d when our Bottles and all we</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter">re filled with Immortalitie.</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter">hen we the&s;e ble&s;&s;ed paths will travel,</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="3 letters">'d with Rubies thick as Gravel</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter">ngs of Diamonds, Saphire Flowers,</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 word"> Walls of Coral, Pearly Bowers:</L>
<L>From thence to Heavens Bribele&s;s Hall,</L>
<L>Where no corrupted voices braul.</L>
<L>No Con&s;cience moulded into Gold,</L>
<L>Nor forg'd Accu&s;er bought or &s;old.</L>
<L>No Cau&s;e deferr'd, no vain &s;pent Journey,</L>
<L>There Chri&s;t alone's the Kings Attourney</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter">ho pleads for all without degrees,</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter">nd he hath Angels, but no Fees.</L>
<L>And when the twelve grand million Jury</L>
<L>Of all my Sins, will in a fury,</L>
<L>Again&s;t my Soul black Verdict give,</L>
<L>Chri&s;t pleads his Death, and then I live.</L>
<L>Be thou my &s;peaker, taintle&s;s pleader,</L>
<L>Unblotted Lawyer, true Proceeder.</L>
<L>Thou give&s;t Salvation even for Alms,</L>
<L>Not with a bribed Lawyers palms.</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="2 letters">d this is mine eternal plea</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="2 letters">m that made Heav'n Earth and Sea;</L>
